{"tid":853742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工作壓力大　青年跳軌亡","createTime":"2018-10-08T23:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T05:09:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1e890b4bfaadef5a806aa722a7c88968ad4c7e36","tid":853742,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T23:53:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181009/20517906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181009%2F20517906&d=CibHFg8IZnIlajm27DXBW49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=299e091c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181009%2F20517906&h=3a1b004a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181009/20517906</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月09日 <br />\n<br />\n工作壓力大　青年跳軌亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181009/large/09la8p02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181009%2Flarge%2F09la8p02.jpg&h=1cd05297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n移送遺體後，港鐵職員落路軌檢查。 <br />\n周鴻熙攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名任職運輸的23歲青年，昨晨在港鐵東鐵綫粉嶺站墮軌，救護員到場證實他當場不治，警方其後相信主因為工作壓力不開心而輕生，案件無可疑。其間太和站來往上水站的服務一度暫停約1小時，港鐵安排接駁巴士疏導乘客。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n粉嶺站受影響<br />\n<br />\n墮軌身亡男子姓龐，據悉，他去年大學畢業後投身運輸業，曾透露有工作壓力。港鐵表示，翻查閉路電視錄影片段，顯示該青年自己跳入路軌。<br />\n<br />\n事發於昨晨8時05分，東鐵綫一列車進入粉嶺站往紅磡方向月台期間，一名男乘客墮軌，車長即時停車，但仍將男子捲入車底，月台長亦按動緊急掣，停止其他列車進出車站。車站職員到場處理，並通知車務控制中心報警及通知消防。<br />\n<br />\n受事故影響，粉嶺站閘機暫時關閉，沿線車站亦擠滿乘客，港鐵安排免費接駁巴士行走太和站至上水站；為避免大圍站過於擠迫，馬鞍山綫曾相應調整至5分鐘一班車。<br />\n<br />\n約一個小時後，東鐵綫及馬鞍山綫列車服務陸續回復正常<br />\n<br />\n■記者周鴻熙、張家豪  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n女嬰嘔奶昏迷不治<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n同獲浸大傑出傳理人獎　陳凱欣參選轉跑道師兄勸勿棄求真"},{"pid":"ebd0347c1510ddfe4c1d349a7f7354892f7e01e7","tid":853742,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T23:55:11.000Z","msg":"運輸？大學生做運輸？"},{"pid":"c256a6aa70594ed41075e51a31cc3adeb31ae806","tid":853742,"uid":169662,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ebd0347c1510ddfe4c1d349a7f7354892f7e01e7","tid":853742,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T23:55:11.000Z","msg":"運輸？大學生做運輸？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T23:57:14.000Z","msg":"運輸都好多崗位既，可能人地機場做control呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3614221621e0ed7f1566089851be0a6a779e3d17","tid":853742,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebd0347c1510ddfe4c1d349a7f7354892f7e01e7","tid":853742,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T23:55:11.000Z","msg":"運輸？大學生做運輸？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T23:58:47.000Z","msg":"係咪嫌其他起步太少錢"},{"pid":"8924e4a6f61920487a0a5f31c22cd581e7ad3484","tid":853742,"uid":88029,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T23:59:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"754e2564cb4d5d665e126c75bacad35ab01270f9","tid":853742,"uid":2267,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T00:19:14.000Z","msg":"我識好幾個消防員放假做pt貨van司機/拆櫃姑爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c4fc48d01c75903151a4961e8970725f6522454","tid":853742,"uid":55488,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T00:23:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60786f92489bf46b5be6795fece38684b55736c6","tid":853742,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebd0347c1510ddfe4c1d349a7f7354892f7e01e7","tid":853742,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T23:55:11.000Z","msg":"運輸？大學生做運輸？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T00:25:51.000Z","msg":"細個唔讀書？"},{"pid":"bfc950b99ce99e756c71a4df9605563706d0